---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---

<div class="bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-y-0 h-full w-full z-20 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="relative h-full">
            <svg class="hidden lg:block absolute left-full transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/4" width="404" height="784" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 404 784">
                <defs>
                    <pattern id="e229dbec-10e9-49ee-8ec3-0286ca089edf" x="0" y="0" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                        <rect x="0" y="0" width="4" height="4" class="text-gray-200" fill="currentColor" />
                    </pattern>
                </defs>
                <rect width="404" height="784" fill="url(#e229dbec-10e9-49ee-8ec3-0286ca089edf)" />
            </svg>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-8 px-4 sm:px-6 md:py-16 lg:px-8 lg:py-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            <span class="block">Нужна консультация ?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500">Наши специалисты подскажут и помогут</p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex">
            <div class="inline-flex rounded-md shadow">
                <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700">Заказать звонок</a>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3 inline-flex">
                <a href={new URL('https://itsect.github.io/specvagonmash/products//contacts')} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border text-base font-medium rounded-md text-gray-400 text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100 border-gray-300 border shadow-sm">Контакты</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="bg-gray-50" aria-labelledby="footer-heading">
    <h2 id="footer-heading" class="sr-only">Footer</h2>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:py-16 lg:px-8">

        <div class="xl:grid xl:grid-cols-3 xl:gap-8">
            <div class="space-y-8 xl:col-span-1">
                <!--<img class="h-10" src="https://tailwindui.com/img/logos/mark.svg?color=gray&shade=300"-->
                <!--     alt="Company name">-->
                <p class="text-base text-gray-500">СПЕЦВАГОНСНАБ – российская компания, являющаяся официальным дилером
                    Parveen, ведущего производителя нефтегазового оборудования</p>

            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 xl:col-span-2 xl:mt-0">
                <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-8">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Решения</h3>
                        <ul role="list" class="mt-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>
                                <a href={new URL('https://itsect.github.io/specvagonmash/products//products')} class="text-base text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">Продукция</a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a href={new URL('https://itsect.github.io/specvagonmash/products//certificates')} class="text-base text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">Сертификаты</a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-8">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-gray-900">Компания</h3>
                        <ul role="list" class="mt-4 space-y-4">
                            <li>
                                <a href={new URL('https://itsect.github.io/specvagonmash/products//about')} class="text-base text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">О компании</a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a href={new URL('https://itsect.github.io/specvagonmash/products//contacts')} class="text-base text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700">Контакты</a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-200 pt-8">
            <p class="text-base text-gray-400 xl:text-center">&copy; {year} – ООО «СПЕЦВАГОНСНАБ»</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>